<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Montgomery </h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Montgomery is located in both ward 1 and 7, is represented by Dale Hodges and Druh Farrell respectively.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">Montgomery is located in the Calgary-Bow riding, represented by Alana Delong and federally in the Calgary West riding, represented by Ron Anders.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Montgomery homes are mostly made up of residential attached and detached single-family (bungalow, two storey), which make up around 71.8% of the market, with the remaining 28.2% being apartments and condominiums.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Approximately 37.9% of homes are occupied by rental tenants. These figures come from statistics gathered in 2006, and may not be completely accurate to the current state of the community.</p>
        </div>
